{"lastModified":1771253306797,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::68cc5210-3744-11f0-889c-13ca00081512","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nStep aboard PROMITHEAS, a luxurious Beneteau Oceanis 51.1 sailing yacht, built in 2022 and moored at the vibrant Marina Alimos in Greece. Designed for comfort and performance, this modern yacht is the ideal choice for unforgettable sailing adventures in the stunning Greek islands.\n\nWith space to accommodate up to 11 guests, Promitheas offers versatile sleeping arrangements, including 4 double cabins, 1 double cabin with a bunk bed and 1 single cabin (for the skipper).\n\nThis yacht is equipped with 3 toilets with showers, ensuring privacy and convenience for all guests. The galley is fully equipped with essentials like a fridge, oven, cooker, sink, and kitchen utensils.\n\nKey Features:\nSailing Excellence: Featuring a rolling mainsail and bow thruster for smooth navigation.\nComfortable Living: Enjoy the comfort of air conditioning, heating, and a well-designed interior.\nEntertainment Options: Equipped with an audio system and outside speakers to enhance your time on board.\nPractical Additions: Includes a generator, bimini, and other amenities for a hassle-free charter.\nWhether you’re planning a family vacation, a getaway with friends, or a romantic escape, Promitheas ensures a premium sailing experience, combining style, space, and functionality.","blueprint":{"name":"PROMITHEAS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::68cc5210-3744-11f0-889c-13ca00081512::assets::567c0a90-374b-11f0-bb30-f381bac714d3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::68cc5210-3744-11f0-889c-13ca00081512::assets::567af920-374b-11f0-bb30-f381bac714d3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::68cc5210-3744-11f0-889c-13ca00081512::assets::567bbc70-374b-11f0-bb30-f381bac714d3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::68cc5210-3744-11f0-889c-13ca00081512::assets::563ba630-374b-11f0-bb30-f381bac714d3/{image